{"tid":2324518,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿迪達教Auba：心如止水可破入球荒","createTime":"2020-12-14T04:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T05:41:32.000Z","uid":133787,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c74c8b307f760ccd6ecc65d80fe0fc64337362","tid":2324518,"uid":133787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:06:38.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】阿仙奴射手奧巴美揚陷入低迷，教練阿迪達勸告對方不要想太多。<br />\n奧巴美揚（Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang）在對上2個英超球季都轟入22球，但今季頭11場僅入2球，當中有1球更來自12碼。 阿迪達（Mikel Arteta）認為，Auba陷入球荒有時候因為他沒有平靜的心境：「這Auba這樣的射手一定要自然一點，不用想太多，跟隨自己的觸覺，在正確時刻做出選擇，用正確的腳，把球放在需要的地方。」 奧巴美揚當然是阿仙奴的王牌，但阿迪達也知道不能只靠他去爭入球：「當你有球員在禁區，你需要另一位球員去鋪橋搭路，所以你需要有球員來幫Auba，然後事情才變得自然，因為壓力小了。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/sports/阿迪達教auba-心如止水可破入球荒-071119940.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fsports%2F%E9%98%BF%E8%BF%AA%E9%81%94%E6%95%99auba-%E5%BF%83%E5%A6%82%E6%AD%A2%E6%B0%B4%E5%8F%AF%E7%A0%B4%E5%85%A5%E7%90%83%E8%8D%92-071119940.html&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725EZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=26079c92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/sports/阿迪達教auba-心如止水可破入球荒-071119940.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />破了！"},{"pid":"0675fe94c86468861534ab6a72e9978c8d669bb7","tid":2324518,"uid":14241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:58:12.000Z","msg":"達蛇好心循循善誘比人b害返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdea987bc40f2f4e1f952156ff00d3df3ae7b182","tid":2324518,"uid":196552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T05:20:37.000Z","msg":"達蛇有料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442d327850301d784ce9a211be2dda936c3fd1d5","tid":2324518,"uid":60524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T05:41:32.000Z","msg":"講漏句都死 用正確的腳冇講個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}